<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>You've been invited to the Memberry admin team</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            color: #334155;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #16a34a 0%, #15803d 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 32px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0 0 8px 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .welcome-message {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin: 0;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 32px;
        }
        .invite-box {
            background: #f0fdf4;
            border: 2px solid #bbf7d0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 24px;
            margin: 24px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .role-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #16a34a;
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 12px;
            border-radius: 999px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: capitalize;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 32px 0;
        }
        .claim-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #16a34a;
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f8fafc;
            padding: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #64748b;
            border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container { margin: 0 16px; border-radius: 0; }
            .header, .content { padding: 24px 20px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>You're invited to the admin team</h1>
            <p class="welcome-message">Memberry platform administration</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="invite-box">
                <h2 style="margin: 0 0 16px 0; color: #16a34a;">Admin access granted</h2>
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px;">
                    You've been invited to administer Memberry as
                    <span class="role-badge">{{role}}</span>.
                </p>
            </div>

            <p>This invitation is tied to <strong>{{email}}</strong>. To activate your
            access, sign in to the Memberry admin app with that email, then claim your
            invitation. Your account is linked the first time you claim.</p>

            <div class="button-container">
                <a href="{{claimUrl}}" class="claim-button">Claim admin access</a>
            </div>

            <p>If the button doesn't work, sign in to the admin app and open the claim
            link. If you weren't expecting this invitation, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Memberry</strong><br>
            Association membership management for healthcare professionals</p>
            <p>This is an automated message. Please do not reply to this email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
